<br>
1. Do returning the notes, words, and spells/bindings always result in the same rewards when returned to the appropriate Sage?<br>
<br>
2. There doesn't appear to be a valid level 44 word/rune combine, but has anyone tried for a level 16, 20, or 24 combine? I'm thinking that there should be one more valid word/rune combine, but level ( circle ) wasn't specified for this part.<br>
<br>
3. For the magical artifacts, since the PGT results in an abjuration binding, I'm thinking that there might be four other items that yield the other bindings - alteration, conjuration, divination, evocation. These should be from artifacts whose spells can be cast by PCs ( but as mentioned may not exist as the abjuration binding comes from an item with an alteration spell ). Assuming these things are working in fives, there might be three other items that yield spells that can't be cast by PCs. Any thoughts on whether the total number of combinable artifacts should be five, ten, or some other number?<br>
<br>
