<br>
2. The lvl 44 word/rune seems to be broken at the present time ( unless it was fixed with todays patch ).<br>
<br>
3. According to the conversation with Sage Xelrin:<br>
<br>
It is my conjecture that some of the magic may be extracted from <br>
these items in order to further our magical repetoire. Even in the case <br>
where an object has a spell that we already have access to, I believe the <br>
binding used to tie the magic to the object could be useful as well. <br>
<br>
So the results for the artifacts combine will be either a spell or a binding.<br>
<br>
